</svg><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">VRR 不同于自适应垂直同步（Adaptive V-Sync 或 late V-Sync），后者根据帧率动态打开或关闭垂直同步。</p></div></div></div>
</div>
</div></div>
</div></section><section id="preferred-refresh-rate"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h3 class="title"><span class="title">首选刷新率</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents pagewide"><p class="p">指定首选刷新率以保持最佳画质。</p></div></div>
</div></section>
</div>
</div></section><section id="scale"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup pagewide"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">缩放</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents pagewide"><p class="p">缩放设置可增大屏幕上显示的对象的大小，以匹配您的显示器的密度，使其更易读。选择<span class="gui">100%</span>或<span class="gui">200%</span>。</p></div></div>
</div></section><section class="links" role="navigation"><div class="inner">
